quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  4,114,"MoЖҙЖҙere alaa e ko heewi e haala maЙ“Й“e kaЙ“e gun- ndata hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en, si wanaa kan haala yamirayka ittugol sadaka, maa moЖҙЖҙere nde diina kan tinndini e mun maa moЖҙЖҙiЕӢtingol hakkunde pooЙ—ondirЙ“e. Kala huuwirЙ—o Й—um Й—aЙ“Й“ugol welayee Alla on, arma Men Okka mo baraaji mawndi."
  4,115,"Kala lunndiiЙ—o NulaaЙ—o on e kon ko o addi Й“aawo nde peewal ngal feeГұannde mo, o jokki laawol goo ko wanaa laawol gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, Men Acciday mo e ko o suЙ“ii kon o majjira sawaaba on sabu Й—uurnagol goonga kan, Men Naadoya mo yiite Jahannama, nge bonii ruttorde !"
  4,116,"Pellet, Alla YawtaЕӢtaa kafidugol Mo e goЙ—Й—um, O Naaday sirkoowo on yiite, Himo Yawtana ko jaasi Й—um e geddi wonannde on Mo O Muuyiri ЖҒural e Yurmeende Makko. Kala o kafiduЙ—o e Alla goЙ—Й—o goo, gomЙ—ii on Й—on ooГұorike e goonga kan ooГұannde woЙ—Й—iinde ; tawde o fotnii TaguЙ—o On e tagaaЙ—o on."
  4,117,"KO ЖҒen sirkooЙ“e rewata, Й“e rewida Й—um e Alla, si wanaa sanamuuji rewЙ—iniraaЙ—i inЙ—e rewЙ“e ; wano Laata, e 'Uzzaa, Й—i lorrataa Й—i nafataa. ЖҒe alaa e rewude ka haqiiqa, si wanaa seytaniiru yaltundu e Й—oftaare Alla ; tawde ko ndun yamiri Й“e rewugol sanamu."
  4,118,"Ko Й—um si Alla WoЙ—Й—iniri ndu e Yurmeende Makko nden, ndun seytaaniiru huЙ—anii Joomi mayru ndu wi'i: "Ma mi jogitoyo e jeyaaЙ“e Maa Й“en geЙ“al anndangal, ngal mi majjinoyta e goonga kan."
  4,119,"Ma mi faloЙ“e gaay e laawol focciingol ngol, ma mi yelinyЙ“e yela fenaande ko no cuЙ—inana Й“e majjere nden, ma mi yamiroyЙ“e taygol noppi neemoraaЙ—i Й—in fii harmingol ko Alla Dagini kon e majji, ma mi yamiroyЙ“e waylugol tagu Alla ngun". Kala on jogitorЙ—o seytaane giЙ—o, gomЙ—ii haray on Й—on sooyii sooyannde Й“anngunde."
  4,120,"Seytaande no foda Й“e penaale, himo yelina Й“e mehre, o alaa e yelinnde Й“e si wanaa mehre."
  4,121,"ЖҒen jokkuЙ“e Й—ate seytaane Й—en e kon ko mbo fida- taЙ“e, ГұiiЙ“irde maЙ“Й“e nden ko ka yiite Jahannama, Й“e heЙ“ataa gaay e magge moolorde."